OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FWhen you sit down with Lisa Vidal and
OL,8,FDiana-Marie Riva, you are struck by
OL,9,Ftheir energy, warmth and fun.
OL,11,FBut make no mistake, these two Latino
OL,12,Factresses are deadly serious about
OL,13,Fchanging an industry they say ignores
OL,14,Fa community that makes up nearly half
OL,15,Fthe population of Los Angeles County.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FBetween them, they have enjoyed
OL,8,Fsuccess in high-profile TV shows like
OL,9,FER, but ask them if they think they
OL,10,Fshould have got more work, and you get
OL,11,Fa definite yes, wrapped in some choice
OL,12,Flanguage as well.
OL,14,FThe two actresses decided to take
OL,15,Fthings into their own hands, creating
OL,16,FLatinos Acting Up, an organisation
OL,17,Fsupporting those in the industry,
OL,18,Ffighting to get a foot in the door.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FDiana gives me some recent statistics
OL,8,Fabout Latino representation in LA,
OL,9,Fsaying there has never been more than
OL,10,F7% of lead or co-leading roles going
OL,11,Fto actors in their community.
OL,13,FLatino and Hispanic people make up
OL,14,F48.8% of the population of Los Angeles
OL,15,FCounty, according to the latest census
OL,16,Fdata.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
