CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FThey take particular aim at
OL,8,Fstereotyping by filmmakers, despairing
OL,9,Fat being offered roles as maids, drug
OL,10,Fdealers or their girlfriends, and
OL,11,Fprostitutes.
OL,13,F"We are not saying they do not exist
OL,14,Fin our community", says Lisa. "But so
OL,15,Fdo doctors and lawyers." Their
OL,16,Forganisation has opened new branches
OL,17,Fin the US, with more requests coming
OL,18,Fin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
