CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FThey are not the only ones calling for
OL,8,FHollywood to give Latino workers a
OL,9,Ffair chance in front of and behind the
OL,10,Fcamera.
OL,12,FBrazilian star Wagner Moura is the
OL,13,Ffirst man from his country to get a
OL,14,Fbest actor Oscar nomination.
OL,16,FHis film The Secret Agent is about an
OL,17,Facademic on the run from persecution
OL,18,Fduring the military dictatorship in
OL,19,FBrazil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FHe says the Latino acting population
OL,8,Fmust simply say no when offered roles
OL,9,Fthat perpetuate stereotypes about them.
OL,11,FMoura does recognise the significance
OL,12,Fof the nominations for him and the
OL,13,Ffilm, and says he is gratified at the
OL,14,Fconversations that have opened up
OL,15,Fsurrounding The Secret Agent.
OL,17,FHe adds that the films setting in an
OL,18,Fauthoritarian regime should also serve
OL,19,Fas a warning from history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
