SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FHis belief that the Latino and
OL,8,FHispanic communities should take on
OL,9,Fthe responsibility of changing the
OL,10,Findustry so it is more equitable for
OL,11,Fthem is one shared by the Nosotros
OL,12,Forganisation in LA.
OL,14,FFounded by the legendary Mexican actor
OL,15,FRicardo Montalban, it aims to offer
OL,16,Fsupport to people from the community
OL,17,Fwishing to be a part of the creative
OL,18,Findustries.
OL,26,@wD@Prp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
