PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FThe late actor had a Theatre named
OL,8,Fafter him, the only Latino in
OL,9,FHollywood so far to have had this
OL,10,Fhonour bestowed.
OL,12,FAnd in a difficult climate, made worse
OL,13,Fby President Trump's announcement of
OL,14,Fcuts to diversity, equity and
OL,15,Finclusion funding, which has also
OL,16,Fimpacted the film industry, the
OL,17,Forganisation is continuing Montalban's
OL,18,Fwork, offering workshops and
OL,19,Fmentorships to industry hopefuls.
OL,26,@yD@crp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
