PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773349951
OL,3,CLatino actors fight for change in a
OL,4,CHollywood still perpetuating
OL,5,Cstereotypes
OL,7,FThe ICE raids and protests around the
OL,8,FUS in recent months may have given the
OL,9,Fcommunity some reason to be worried
OL,10,Fabout raising its head above the
OL,11,Fparapet.
OL,13,FBut with the lack of opportunity for
OL,14,FLatinos long having been an issue in
OL,15,Fthe US, this year's Oscars gives them
OL,16,Fa chance to remind the industry that
OL,17,Fthey are there and keen to get the
OL,18,Fchance to work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
